{"id":681752,"title":"01｜学习的本质、误区及原则","content":"","comments":[{"had_liked":false,"id":380844,"user_name":"进化菌","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1276861,"ip_address":"广东","ucode":"B30A5F78BB4171","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/7b/bd/ccb37425.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1694274070,"is_pvip":true,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":4,"score":2,"product_id":100610501,"comment_content":"结构化思考的学习，学习的本质是“为学之道，必本于思”。\n\n学习的误区：学习只是学习（一味的吸收知识，死记硬背），阅读就是学习（大量阅读不是学习的全部），知识就是力量（知识范围广，不一定是力量；只停留在某些阶段的知识也未必能发挥作用），学习是自己的事（封闭自我）。\n\n学习的三条基本原则：重视先前的知识（温故而知新），概念化的组织和使用知识，知道如何管理自己的学习活动。","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":391353,"user_name":"Roway","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1060967,"ip_address":"陕西","ucode":"65AF589142AB6C","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/30/67/a1e9aaba.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1718078740,"is_pvip":true,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":1,"score":2,"product_id":100610501,"comment_content":"课程的课件ppt有吗？","like_count":0}]}